S is built on top of Ethereum. Finally, MIS\nis implemented on two testbeds and is available online as the open-source\nsystem. The first testbed consists of 4 physical servers located in the UK and\nMalaysia while the second is made up of 200 virtual machines (VMs) spread over\n26 countries across all 5 continents on Google Cloud.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 9 Jan 2023 17:24:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 6 May 2023 03:31:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-09"}
