 both ionized and molecular gas). With this paper we\nrelease the full catalogue of strong line fluxes and derived properties,\nproviding a rich database for a broad variety of ISM studies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 10 Jan 2023 06:46:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-25"}
